HEADWORD: Black pudding
<hw>Black" pud"ding</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>. <def>A kind of sausage made of
blood, suet, etc., thickened with meal.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>And fat black <qex>puddings</qex>, -- proper food,⟦br⟧
For warriors that delight in blood.</q>
<rj><qau>Hudibras.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Black Rod</ent>⟦br⟧
